<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038539" n="167v"/>
    <p><lb/>Ad ambas Tuas <rs type="letters" key="B_1718-12-19_991170517038805501 B_1718-12-22_991170517038505501">epistolas</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1718-12-19">19.</date> et <date when="1718-12-22">22.</date> hujus mensis scriptas citius non
        <lb/>potui respondere, propter alias <rs type="letters">epistolas</rs><!-- Diese Briefe konnten nicht nachgewiesen werden -->, quas heri <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs>
                              <lb/>misi. Petis demonstrationem hujus theorematis, <hi rend="u">quod vires centri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quibus corpora gyrantia in circumferentiis</hi> (circulorum) <hi rend="u">reti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nentur sint in composita ratione ex quadratis velocitatum, et ex
                              <lb/>simplici reciproca diametrorum, hoc est, ex simplici directa con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vexitatum seu flexurarum</hi>. Hoc theorema primum est ex illis<del>,</del>
        <lb/><del>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Hugenius </del>decem theorematis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118639749">Hugenius</rs> in Calce <!-- ToDo: in Zotero aufnehmen und verlinken https://www.e-rara.ch/zut/content/search/3347187?query=horologium%20oscillatorium Es handelt sich um die drei letzten Seiten, 159-161 (https://www.e-rara.ch/zut/content/zoom/3347366) --><rs type="biblio">Horo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1038540" n="168r"/>
<lb break="no"/>logii sui Oscillatorii</rs> proposuit; inveniturque ejus demonstratio
                              <lb/>apud omnes qui de viribus centripetis et centrifugis scripserunt,
        <lb/>nominatim in <rs type="biblio"><abbr>opusc.</abbr><!-- ToDo: In Zotero aufnehmen und verlinken https://doi.org/10.3931/e-rara-4066 Kontrollieren, ob es sich beim Link um die Erstausgabe handelt --> <abbr>posth.</abbr></rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118639749">Hugenii</rs>; vide etiam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtoni</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_MF4GV2BJ"><choice><orig>prin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cipia</orig><reg>Principia</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>pag.</abbr> 38<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <abbr>coroll.</abbr> 1<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><supplied>,</supplied> <abbr>prop.</abbr> 4. En tamen hic demonstrationem vul<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>garem! Gyretur corpus in circumferentia circuli <formula>AECF</formula>, sitque
        <lb/>arcus<figure facs="1038540_01.jpg" hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><figDesc>Darstellung eines sich im Kreis drehenden Körpers.</figDesc><note type="editorial"></note></figure> <formula>AE</formula> qui tempore quam minimo describitur.
                              <lb/>Si vis centripeta non ageret in corpus, hoc ea
                              <lb/>cum velocitate quam habet in puncto <formula>A</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que per totum circulum eadem est<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> pergeret mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>veri per tangentem <formula>AD</formula>, et eodem tempore, quo per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>curritur arcus <formula>AE</formula> perveniret ad punctum <formula>D</formula>; ergo
                              <lb/>ut corpus in orbita circulari detineatur,<del>ef</del> oportet ut vis centripe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ta detrudat corpus ex puncto <formula>D</formula> in punctum <formula>E</formula>, quare spatium <formula>DE</formula> tan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam effectus proprius ipsius vis centripet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentare potest quan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>titatem hujus vis;<del><gap/></del> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea recta <formula>AD</formula> tanquam spatium, quod
                              <lb/>mobile motu uniformi dato tempore sine vi centripeta describe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ret, repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentare potest velocitatem corporis in puncto <formula>A</formula>. Jam
        <lb/>vero per 36. 3.<note type="comment">Buch III, Proposition 36 (Satz des Euklid).</note> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118638955"><abbr>Eucl.</abbr></rs> quadratum ipsius <formula>AD=DF\times DE =</formula> (propter
        <lb/>arcum <formula>AE</formula> infinite parvum) <formula>EF\times DE</formula>, id est, quadratum velocita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale rectangulo diametri <formula>EF</formula> et vis centripet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>; unde con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stat veritas theorematis. Secundum quod petis demonstrari, nempe
                              <lb/>quod convexitates seu curvatur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint semper diametris reciproce
                              <lb/>proportionales, non opus habet demonstratione; h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c enim propo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sitio nihil aliud continet quam definitionem<del>, siqu</del> curvatur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>sive convexitatis, siquidem illos circulos appellamus magis cur<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vos qui minorem habent diametrum, et vicissim; et <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stima<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mus curvedinem sive convexitatem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> parvitate diametri; sic li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nea recta est circulus omnium minime curvus, cujus diameter
                              <lb/>nempe esset infinita; Hinc etiam est quod curvedines reliqua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum curvarum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimamus <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> radio circuli osculatoris, nam
                              <lb/>in puncto osculi arcus minimus curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> congruit cum arcu minimo
                              <pb facs="1038541" n="168v"/>
<lb/>circuli osculatoris, adeoque utraque <add>curva</add> ibidem eandem habet convexi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatem. Tertio petis ut considerem, an vera sit h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtoni</rs> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>positio: <hi rend="u">Eorum corporum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt ejusdem generis et virtutis
                              <lb/>quanto est quodque minutius tanto fortiorem habet pro ratione
                              <lb/>magnitudinis su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vim attrahentem</hi>. Ego puto esse veram propter
        <lb/>rationem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtono</rs><del> ibidem</del> in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_KGWAEINJ">Optica</rs> allegatam, nempe corpor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>ejusdem generis<del> plus</del> magnitudines in minori ratione crescere
                              <lb/>quam <add>crescant</add> ipsorum vires attractrices, quamvis in quanam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cise
                              <lb/>ratione crescant nemo fortassis determinabit. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c ad pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pua <rs type="letters" key="B_1718-12-19_991170517038805501 B_1718-12-22_991170517038505501">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ultim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> contenta respondere debui. Heri
        <lb/>accepi <rs type="letter" key="letter">epistolam</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzero</rs>, in qua sua Tibi offert ob<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sequia. <add>Significavit mihi se</add> <subst><del>H</del><add>h</add></subst>abe<subst><del>t</del><add>re</add></subst> sub prelo <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_6CBDPU2E">Methodum Graminum</rs></hi>, quam
        <lb/>brevi sequetur ipsa <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_FTUNNEH6">Historia</rs>, quam dedicare vult <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et 
    <lb/><abbr>Exc.</abbr> <rs type="persons" key="GND GND GND">Reformatoribus</rs>. Nulla amplius prostant exemplaria
        <lb/>dissertationum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118607308">fratris</rs> ejus <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio">de Cerva Cornuta</rs></hi>, <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio">de Surdo au<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>diente</rs></hi>, de <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio">Usu Matheseos in Medicina</rs></hi>;<!-- Liste Bibliographie Scheuchzer: https://ub-mediawiki.ub.unibas.ch/bernoulli/index.php/SchriftenverzeichnisJohIBJSch --> promisit tamen
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rere apud amicos, et reliqua tum sua, tum <rs type="person" key="GND">fratris</rs> scri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pta mihi mittere. Cum me toties moneas de perficiendo
    <lb/><rs type="biblio">opere Mathematico</rs> <hi rend="u">pro Tua utilitate et pro meo honore
                              <lb/>et gloria</hi>; ideo Te nunc semel pro semper rogatum cupio,
                              <lb/>ut Tibi persuadeas, me facturum omnia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> possum pro
                              <lb/>tua utilitate, et qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> debeo pro honore meo tuendo apud
                              <lb/>omnes veros<del> rerum</del> virtutis <subst><del>exi</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add></subst>stimatores. Malo autem pro
                              <lb/><hi rend="u">non sapiente</hi> haberi ab illis<subst><del> (</del><add>, </add></subst>qui ipsi stulti sunt<subst><del>) </del><add>, </add></subst> quam
                              <lb/>facere, ut faciunt maxima pars Italorum. An futuris
        <lb/><date>Bacchan<subst><del>i</del><add>a</add></subst>libus</date> <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetias</rs> ibo, dicere non possum, res pendet <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>conditione aliqua, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> si deficiet suspendetur etiam hoc iter.
        <lb/>Spero Te misisse <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3169070">Romam</rs> <rs type="letter" key="LetterID">epistolam</rs> meam ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156417392">Fridericum
            <lb/>Gutt</rs>. <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenus</rs> mecum expostulavit rogans, num Tibi<del>sc</del> per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>scripserim ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipse mecum de Te locutus fuerat; Te enim
                              <pb facs="1038542" n="169r"/>
<lb/><del>ita </del>eo modo scripsisse <add>ait</add> <rs type="letter" key="letter">litteras</rs> Tuas, ut ex illis apparere possit, Te
                              <lb/>aliqua <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me audivisse. Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> res mihi magnopere displicet, et rogo
        <lb/>ut posthac cautius agas.</p><closer><salute>Vale.</salute> Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> ipso <date when="1718-12-25">Die Natali</date>,
                              <lb/>quem Tibi cum reliquis festis totoque futuro a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o felicem apprecor.</closer>
</div>
